{"tid":1228531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】身在台灣心在港 蔣雅文明日返港參加反惡法遊行","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:23:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68bc0993a04ea7947eb92da76d7334894304456e","tid":1228531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"蔣雅文在IG上載了一張選擇了6月16日的日曆照片，而相中更有「回家」這兩個字，她留言表示：「如果你跟我一樣，這星期經歷了心痛難過和羞愧，6.16就是治癒自己的時刻。」<br />\n而今日蔣雅文再出post：「當一個社會頻率變沉重，需要團結產生高頻共振，簡單來說就是信念，所以，明天誰要來陪我曬太陽健行散心？」一眾網民看到後，均紛紛留言說：「明天見」、「守護家園，路上見」、「我們都在，聽日見」。<br />\n<br />\n民陣6.16反惡法遊行<br />\n日期：6月16日（日）<br />\n集合地點：維園草地<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合、3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：維園至金鐘添美道立法會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59720564?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ZSlwGnuAuCBajNRB9UL73iuZqra6jDTzxfICEtmmLnecd90F0l9j8-jY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59720564%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ZSlwGnuAuCBajNRB9UL73iuZqra6jDTzxfICEtmmLnecd90F0l9j8-jY&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe27Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=000c8796\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59720564%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0ZSlwGnuAuCBajNRB9UL73iuZqra6jDTzxfICEtmmLnecd90F0l9j8-jY&h=9b713907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59720564?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0ZSlwGnuAuCBajNRB9UL73iuZqra6jDTzxfICEtmmLn